title: SSU rRNA amplicon sequencing of mixed natural samples : mock community for QC
design_description: Whole-community (>0.2uM) seawater samples were amplified with 515Y/926R primers using PCR primers that contained Illumina adapters/barcodes. Resulting data includes both 16S and 18S sequences, which should be separated bioinformatically prior to ASV/OTU analysis. Data here has been demultiplexed allowing no mismatches to the Illumina reverse index (bcl2fastq) and the forward barcode (cutadapt).

Data here has been demultiplexed allowing no mismatches to the Illumina reverse index (bcl2fastq) and the forward barcode (cutadapt).
